{"tid":355530,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"綜緩大陸新移民豪學樂器養貓呻窮","createTime":"2017-08-11T11:04:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-11T13:16:18.000Z","uid":17250,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"41a7f04c6ba55d28e9e5c7ba6f5cc556452cf40d","tid":355530,"uid":17250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T11:04:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/CJZ3OlfT6-M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FCJZ3OlfT6-M&d=LqU%2Biehar3Y0COcM%2FKLbcNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=651c8e99\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/CJZ3OlfT6-M</a><br />\n<br />\n話自己基層冇錢<br />\n綜緩月入15k，窮人學兩個女<br />\n兩個女都至少中學啦，啊媽用照顧個女為由冇工作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又俾個女學琴學樂器，重去北京表演<br />\n呻自己一個月用兩千交學費但又係留言話免費學<br />\n根本係大話連篇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住又養三隻貓又cool牙，但又話自己有哮喘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第二個家庭個老豆重勁<br />\n下下話資源分配，冇錢俾個女去北京<br />\n如果真係冇錢，就唔應該生兩個<br />\n第二胎係仔好明係想生仔先追既<br />\n個仔重話家姐有得學，自己就冇<br />\n冇能力就唔應該生，窮人生仔正仆街<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/11/185340_9e8084b6611b92047f41219176124549.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F11%2F185340_9e8084b6611b92047f41219176124549.jpg&h=fbd36805&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/11/185346_b49746d394203c7e144f84c1fa97cd9c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F11%2F185346_b49746d394203c7e144f84c1fa97cd9c.jpg&h=810daaae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/11/185409_ac612